h3. assertIsEmptyArray{*}(any obj1,\[String message\])
Determines if the obj1 is an array with no elements. {code:title=assertIsEmptyArray()} <cffunction name="demoAssertIsEmptyArray"> <cfset assertIsEmptyArray(myObject1)> </cffunction> {code}
h3. assertIsEmptyQuery{*}(any obj1,\[String message\])
